title: Bring It S01E04 Baby Doll Dont Mean Baby WS DSR x264-[NY2] mp4
description:
The Dancing Dolls get their pint-sized counterparts, the Baby Dancing Dolls, to compete in their place so they can focus on developing a secret weapon to defeat their biggest rival, the Prancing Tigerettes. Meanwhile, Selena's bad behavior threatens her daughter's future on the team; and the squad members question Kayla's leadership as captain.
